metadata.name: BABY EROS
metadata.description: Baby Eros was enjoying his childhood, unaware of what was going to happen to him. He didn't know that when he grew up, he would burn in the fire of love. Growing up is a painful process. It is necessary to accept all the experiences, pains and guests on the way. It is easier to reach the planet Mars than to reach it on your own. We have to take risks to reach ourselves and grow. Like Eros who accepts to burn in the fire of love--
